metadata.name: Cosplay Membership Pass
metadata.description: A Cosplay Membership Pass is step one in getting you set up as an owner in the Cos ecosystem. You will use this Membership Pass as a mint pass to our genesis drop, however, it is more than a mint pass. Your Membership Pass will be the key to how you connect to and derive value from the Cos ecosystem. You can think of it as an all-access pass to everything Cosplay. We highly recommend you hold onto your Membership Pass tight! More scenarios will be expanded in future, e.g. airdrops, cooperation, derivatives.Weâ€™re limiting membership to 2,100.
